title: The Suicide Club
description: THE SUICIDE CLUB is the story of what happens when bored, drugged-out rich kids decide to dress up and play games. Mariel Hemingway stars as an heiress, Sasha Michaels, who has been teetering on the edge of a mental breakdown ever since the suicide of her brother. Her friend Cam (Lenny Henry) takes her to a private costume party in a gothic mansion, where the guests play a card game in which the winner must swallow a poisonous drink. Naturally, Sasha wants to play. (TV Guide)
